<%- await include('email-doctype'); %>
  <html xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml" lang="en">
  <%- await include('email-head', {title: title}); %>

    <body class="body" style="
      padding: 0;
      margin: 0;
      display: block;
      background: #ffffff;
      -webkit-text-size-adjust: none;
    " bgcolor="#ffffff">
      <div class="container">
        <%- await include('email-banner'); %>
          <table>
            <tr>
              <td style="border-bottom: 1px solid #e7e7e7">
                <p style="text-align: center">
                  <strong>This is an automated email. No response is required.</strong>
                </p>
                <p>
                  Your employee, <%= contact.first_name %>
                    <%= contact.last_name %>,
                      has registered to receive a <%= service.milestone %> year
                        <a href="https://longserviceawards.gww.gov.bc.ca">
                          Long Service Award</a>
                        in <%= service.cycle %>.
                </p>
                <p>
                  The Long Service Awards program is open to any full-time,
                  part-time and seasonal employees who have reached a 25, 30, 35, 40,
                  45 or 50-year milestone with the BC Public Service by December 31,
                  <%= service.cycle %>. Employees who have achieved one of these
                    milestones before <%= service.cycle %>, but have not yet been
                      recognized, can also register.
                </p>
                <p>
                  Some recipients may receive a service pin. If applicable, we will send your
                  employee's pin to you in early June so you can present it during Public Service
                  Week.
                </p>
                <h2>Ceremony</h2>
                <p>
                  The <%= service.cycle %> ceremonies will be held in Victoria this fall.
                </p>
                <% let nextCycle=service.cycle + 1 %>
                  <p>
                    If your employee has registered but cannot attend their ceremony, they may be eligible to
                    defer for one year and attend a ceremony in <%= nextCycle %>. In that case, we
                      will courier their award to them in the fall. If they declined their last invitation,
                      this is their final opportunity to attend a ceremony.</p>
                  <p>
                    If your employee contacts you to cancel their registration, please notify us right away at
                    <a href="mailto:LongServiceAwards@gov.bc.ca">LongServiceAwards@gov.bc.ca</a> and inform
                    your <a href="https://longserviceawards.gww.gov.bc.ca/contacts/">ministry contact</a> as soon as
                    possible.
                    Failure to provide a cancellation notice may affect their eligibility to defer to the following
                    year.
                  </p>
                  <h2>Travel and Time Off</h2>
                  <p>
                    Long Service Awards recipients from outside Greater Victoria must
                    be approved to take time off to attend their ceremony. The employee’s organization covers
                    travel costs for the recipient and one guest, including transportation, hotel and
                    meals.
                  </p>
                  <p>
                    For Victoria-based employees, their organization covers taxi costs to and from
                    the ceremony. Victoria-based recipients should be released from work by 2:00
                    pm on their ceremony day with no loss of pay. For front-line workers, please
                    ensure coverage is arranged in advance.
                  </p>
                  <p>
                    If you have any questions, please contact your
                    <a href="https://longserviceawards.gww.gov.bc.ca/contacts/">Long Service Award contact</a>.
                  </p>
                  <p>
                    Your Long Service Awards team
                  </p>
                  <%- await include('email-footer'); %>
              </td>
            </tr>
          </table>
      </div>
    </body>

  </html>